<br>
How do you other RL's handle supplies for a raid? I'm talking about reimbursing players for reagents etc. Do you get everyone to let you know what they have used afterwards? Bring a supply to the raid and dish them out at the start? Do you even bother unless someone mentions it?<br>
<br>
