<br>
Then I sell the loot that is not considered for the scarab bank (i. e. gems others than BD and other vendor trash) and trade them the amount from the money I got by selling. The rest of the money then goes to Nagg (the scarab mule).<br>
<br>
Only on special occasions I bring some of the required components:<br>
- port stones if we go to Sky or Hate<br>
- coffins if we go to Sky or Chardok<br>
<br>
